data.description: Live in & rent opportunity! Very well maintained 2 family home offering over 2800 sq ft of living space. Each unit is 3 bed 1 bath with eat kitchens, formal dining rooms, spacious bedrooms, enclosed porch on each floor, fresh paint throughout, new carpet, hardwood flooring, updated electric, full attic great for storage, CLEAN full basement, 1 car attached garage & plenty of parking. Separate gas electric & heat. Located in the heart of the city only a few minutes from route 12, Addison Miller public park & so much more.
